  "text": "Averaging Generalised estimating equations-the outcome in each eye is modelled as a function of the risk factors and the correlation between the fellow eyes is modelled separately and explicitly. [CITATION_1] If used appropriately, these two approaches give similar results in most, but not all, circumstances. They represent an eYcient use of available data.",
